            My hon. Friend the Member for Northavon talked about the first main line&#x2014;London to Bristol. It is the main link for many of my constituents in Frome and the
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_304wh' title='Col. 304WH &mdash; HC Deb 29 January 2003 vol 398 c304WH' name='column_304wh' href='#column_304wh' rel='bookmark'>304WH</a>
